TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MAX (PRD.QTR_PERIOD_BEGIN_DT) AS QTR_PERIOD_BEGIN_DT, MAX (PRD.QTR_PERIOD_END_DT) AS QTR_PERIOD_END_DT, MAX (BCI.DSPN_DT) AS DSPN_DT, MAX (BCI.RBAT_ID) AS RBAT_ID, MAX (BCI.EXTL_SRC_CD) AS EXTL_SRC_CD, MAX (BCI.EXTL_LVL1_ID) AS EXTL_LVL1_ID, MAX (BCI.EXTL_LVL2_ID) AS EXTL_LVL2_ID, MAX (BCI.EXTL_LVL3_ID) AS EXTL_LVL3_ID, SUM (EXT.BASE_DISCNT_AMT) AS BASE_DISCNT_AMT, SUM (EXT.PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT) AS PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT, SUM (EXT.CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT) AS CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT, SUM (EXT.FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT) AS FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT, SUM (EXT.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT) AS PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT, SUM (EXT.ADMN_DISCNT_AMT) AS ADMN_DISCNT_AMT, SUM (BCI.IC_AMT) AS IC_AMT, SUM (BCA.CTRC_FEE_PD_AMT) AS CTRC_FEE_PD_AMT, MAX (BCA.TAX_AMT) AS TAX_AMT, MAX (BCI.MBR_RBAT_DISC_AMT) AS MBR_RBAT_DISC_AMT, MAX (BCA.INSRD_ID) AS INSRD_ID, BCI.CLM_GID AS CLM_GID, MAX (PRD.PERIOD_PARENT_ID) AS PERIOD_PARENT_ID, MAX (PRD.QUARTER_ID) AS QUARTER_ID, BCI.CLM_LVL1_ID AS CLM_LVL1_ID, BCI.CLM_LVL2_ID AS CLM_LVL2_ID, BCI.CLM_TYP_CD AS CLM_TYP_CD, BCI.MED_PYBL_CD AS MED_PYBL_CD, BCI.AP_CO_CD AS AP_CO_CD FROM VRAP.TCUR_INV_PRD CUR INNER JOIN VRAP.VRCIT_MODEL_PRD_STUS PRD ON CUR.QUARTER_ID = PRD.QUARTER_ID AND PRD.MODEL_TYP_CD = 'T' INNER JOIN VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_INV BCI ON BCI.INV_ELIG_DT = PRD.MNTH_PERIOD_END_DT AND BCI.MODEL_TYP_CD = PRD.MODEL_TYP_CD INNER JOIN VRAP.TAPC_CLAIMS_AET AET ON BCI.CLM_GID = AET.CLAIM_ID AND AET.QUARTER_ID = PRD.QUARTER_ID INNER JOIN VRAP.RCIT_BASE_CLM_APC BCA ON AET.CLAIM_ID = BCA.CLM_GID LEFT OUTER JOIN VRAP.TDISCNT_EXT_CLAIM_AET EXT ON AET.HVST_ID = EXT.HVST_ID AND AET.CLAIM_ID = EXT.CLAIM_ID GROUP BY BCI.CLM_GID, BCI.CLM_LVL1_ID, BCI.CLM_LVL2_ID, BCI.CLM_TYP_CD, BCI.MED_PYBL_CD, BCI.AP_CO_CD WITH UR
